source: A Class 350 unit failed at Stafford earlier today. After attention from a fitter, the train can re-enter service. You've arrived at Stafford in a taxi to board the train to run empty to Wolverhampton, where you will form a northbound service to Crewe.
target: 今天早些时候，一列350型列车在斯塔福德发生故障。经过维修人员的检修，列车已恢复运营。您乘坐出租车抵达斯塔福德，准备登上这列空车前往伍尔弗汉普顿的列车，在那里您将组成一列北行列车前往克鲁。

source: A southbound train has encountered a fault north of here. Therefore, a line block has been granted on the Down and Up Fast lines between Norton Bridge and Basford Hall Jn, which means all traffic will be sharing the slow lines.
target: 一列南行列车在此处以北遭遇故障。因此，诺顿桥站和巴斯福德霍尔枢纽站之间的下行和上行快线已实施线路封闭，这意味着所有列车将共用慢线。

source: A train has encountered a fault and has arrived at Birmingham New St. You must prepare a replacement unit at Soho Depot and take the faulty unit to Wolverhampton.
target: 一列火车发生故障，已抵达伯明翰新街站。您必须在苏豪车辆段准备替换车厢，并将故障车厢运往伍尔弗汉普顿。

source: A wheelflat is the fault on this unit. As a result, Control has requested the train travel no faster than 50mph and for you to meet with a Mobile Operations Manager (MOM) at Down Stour Goods. Depart when ready.
target: 这节车厢发生车轮爆胎故障。因此，控制中心要求列车行驶速度不得超过 50 英里/小时，并请您前往 Down Stour 货运站与移动运营经理 (MOM) 会面。准备就绪后即可出发。

source: Due to a planning error, a local service to Wolverhampton has no driver. This morning, you’ve been called in to drive this service in its entirety, calling at all booked stations. Hopefully, your train won't develop any faults...
target: 由于计划失误，一趟开往伍尔弗汉普顿的本地列车缺少司机。今天早上，您被临时召来驾驶这趟列车，全程停靠所有预定车站。希望您的列车不会出现任何故障……

source: Due to a planning error, the 09:08 departure to Wolverhampton is without a driver. Board the train in front of you and sit in the driver's seat.
target: 由于计划失误，09:08 开往伍尔弗汉普顿的列车没有司机。请您登上前面的列车，并坐在司机座位上。

source: Due to the disruption, Control has requested for your train to be stabled in the centre sidings. Please change ends; stop north of the station; change ends again and stop the No. 1 siding to finish off with.
target: 由于线路中断，控制中心要求您的列车停靠在中央侧线。请换向两端；在车站北侧停车；再次换向两端，并在1号侧线停车完成剩余路程。

source: Due to the high winds and heavy rain, the bridge ahead is currently being evaluated by engineers and technicians. Authority has been given for your train to pass under it at no faster than 5mph. Proceed at 5mph to the end point marked on your HUD.
target: 由于强风暴雨，前方桥梁目前正在接受工程师和技术人员的评估。您的列车已获准以不超过5英里/小时的速度通过桥梁下方。请以5英里/小时的速度行驶至HUD上显示的终点。

source: Great! Now the train is ready to move! Please pull forward and couple to the unit in front of you.
target: 太好了！列车现在可以启动了！请向前行驶，并与前面的车厢连接。

source: Great! Now the train is ready to move! Please pull forward and couple to the unit in front of you.
target: 太好了！列车现在可以启动了！请向前行驶，并与前面的车厢连接。

source: Great! Now the two units are coupled, head to the front of the train and setup the cab. We can then depart for Stafford, where the rear unit will be uncoupled so it can continue along the Trent Valley.
target: 太好了！现在两节车厢已经连接好了，请到列车前端设置驾驶室。之后我们就可以出发前往斯塔福德，在那里后部的车厢将会解挂，以便继续沿着特伦特河谷行驶。

source: Great! Please wait here for a few minutes for a path to Wolverhampton.
target: 太好了！请在这里稍等几分钟，我们会安排前往伍尔弗汉普顿的路线。

source: Great. Now pull forward; couple to the other Class 350 unit in front of you and follow the instructions.
target: 很好。现在向前行驶；与前面的另一台350型机车连接，然后按照指示操作。

source: Great. Please pull forward and couple to the other Class 350 unit in front of you.
target: 好的。请向前行驶，与前面的另一辆350型机车连接。

source: Introduced in the 1950s, AWS (Automatic Warning System) is an audiovisual safety system to indicate to drivers the current state of the next signal and of any upcoming speed reductions.
target: AWS（自动警告系统）于 20 世纪 50 年代推出，是一种视听安全系统，用于向驾驶员指示下一个信号的当前状态以及任何即将发生的减速情况。

target: 遵守限速规定非常重要。如果开始超速，请将主手柄拨到制动位置，施加少量制动力。

source: Last but not least, the Class 350/3 units were built in 2014 to provide more capacity. These are similar to the Class 350/2s with a 2+2 seating arrangement compared to 2+3 and wears an alternative LNWR livery with green stripes on the bodyside.
target: 最后，为了提升运力，350/3型列车于2014年建造。这些列车与350/2型列车类似，但座椅布局为2+2而非2+3，并且车身侧面涂有带有绿色条纹的LNWR涂装。

source: Now that we've arrived at Coseley, please open the left doors.
target: 现在我们已经到达科斯利，请打开左边的门。

source: Now that we've arrived at Coseley, please open the left doors.
target: 现在我们已经到达科斯利，请打开左边的门。

source: Now that we've arrived at Stafford, the two units need to be separated. Please follow the instructions for how to do so.
target: 现在我们已经到达斯塔福德，需要将这两组车分开。请按照说明进行操作。

source: Now that we've arrived at Wolverhampton, please change ends so we can depart with the 13:54 service to Crewe.
target: 既然我们已经到达伍尔弗汉普顿，请换向，以便我们能搭乘 13:54 的列车前往克鲁。

source: Now that we've arrived at the loop, please talk to the MOM to make sure the train can continue.
target: 既然我们已经到达环线，请与列车长联系，确保列车可以继续运行。

source: Now that we've been introduced to the trains, walk down Road 1 to the rear unit and set it up.
target: 现在我们已经了解了火车，请沿着 1 号路走到后面的单元并进行设置。

source: Now that we've been introduced to the trains, walk down Road 1 to the rear unit and set it up.
target: 现在我们已经了解了火车，请沿着 1 号路走到后面的单元并进行设置。

source: Now that you've mastered intercity commuter services and local stopper services, it's time to take charge of the special British Transport Livery Class 350 and work some busy commuter services.
target: 既然你已经掌握了城际通勤服务和本地短途服务，现在是时候驾驶英国交通局涂装的350型特殊列车，执行一些繁忙的通勤服务了。

source: Now the train is setup, we can now depart for Crewe station. Please stop at the Stop board ahead so you can get the signaller's permission to leave the sidings.
target: 列车已准备就绪，我们可以出发前往克鲁车站了。请在前方停车标志处停车，以便获得信号员的许可才能离开侧线。

source: Now the two units are coupled, follow the instructions for shutting down this cab and opening the interconnecting doors between the two units.
target: 现在两个单元已连接，请按照说明关闭此驾驶室并打开两个单元之间的连接门。

source: Now the two units are coupled, follow the instructions for shutting down this cab and opening the interconnecting doors between the two units.
target: 现在两个单元已连接，请按照说明关闭此驾驶室并打开两个单元之间的连接门。

source: Now the two units have been coupled, shut down this cab and open the doors between the two units so passengers can walk through.
target: 现在两节车厢已经连接完毕，关闭驾驶室，打开两节车厢之间的车门，以便乘客可以通行。

source: Now the two units have been separated, we can now continue to Wolverhampton.

source: That's all for this tutorial! Please continue to the second tutorial to learn about the safety systems on the Class 350.
target: 本教程到此结束！请继续学习第二个教程，了解350型列车的安全系统。

source: That's all for this tutorial! Please continue to the second tutorial to learn about the safety systems on the Class 350.
target: 本教程到此结束！请继续学习第二个教程，了解350型列车的安全系统。

source: The Class 350 Electric Multiple Units (EMUs) were constructed between 2004 and 2014 in four batches by Siemens in Germany. The first batch is unique in that it can operate from the 25kV overhead electric wires and the 750V DC third rail. The latter was used in 2009 when they were hired to work Milton Keynes Central to East Croydon services. The other batches can only run on the overhead wires.
target: 350型电力动车组（EMU）由德国西门子公司于2004年至2014年间分四批制造。第一批列车较为特殊，既可使用25千伏架空电线供电，也可使用750伏直流第三轨供电。2009年，这些列车被租用运营米尔顿凯恩斯中心站至东克罗伊登站的线路时，便采用了直流第三轨供电方式。其余批次的列车只能使用架空电线供电。

source: The Crewe to Birmingham route recreates the busy WCML between the historic town of Crewe to the busy city of Birmingham, through Stafford and Wolverhampton. The line carries high speed passenger services out of London to Northern England, Scotland and North Wales.
target: 克鲁至伯明翰线路重现了繁忙的西海岸干线（WCML），连接历史名镇克鲁和繁华的伯明翰市，途经斯塔福德和伍尔弗汉普顿。该线路提供从伦敦开往英格兰北部、苏格兰和北威尔士的高速客运服务。

source: The Driver Reminder Appliance (DRA) is a switch fitted to passenger trains that isolates traction power. This is meant to be used when the train is stationary or is stopped at a red signal.
target: 驾驶员提醒装置（DRA）是安装在客运列车上的一个开关，用于切断牵引电源。该装置用于列车静止或停靠在红灯处时。

source: The Driver Vigilance Device (DVD) is an auditory safety system to ensure the driver is still vigilant by sounding an alarm every sixty seconds. The driver must then lift the DVD pedal below their desk to reset the alarm. Failing to do this will apply the emergency brakes. If the driver moves certain controls (like the power brake controller), the vigilance timer will reset.
target: 驾驶员警觉装置（DVD）是一种听觉安全系统，每隔六十秒发出一次警报，以确保驾驶员保持警觉。驾驶员必须抬起办公桌下方的DVD踏板才能重置警报。如果驾驶员未执行此操作，系统将启动紧急制动。如果驾驶员移动某些控制装置（例如动力制动控制器），警觉计时器将重置。

source: The Driver Vigilance Device (DVD) is an auditory safety system to ensure the driver is still vigilant by sounding an alarm every sixty seconds. The driver must then lift the DVD pedal below their desk to reset the alarm. Failing to do this will apply the emergency brakes. If the driver moves certain controls (like the power brake controller), the vigilance timer will reset.
target: 驾驶员警觉装置（DVD）是一种听觉安全系统，每隔六十秒发出一次警报，以确保驾驶员保持警觉。驾驶员必须抬起办公桌下方的DVD踏板才能重置警报。如果驾驶员未执行此操作，系统将启动紧急制动。如果驾驶员移动某些控制装置（例如动力制动控制器），警觉计时器将重置。

source: The Grand Junction Railway, opened in 1837, connected the city of Birmingham to the Liverpool and Manchester railway. Today, this route is a part of the very busy WCML running from London Euston to Glasgow Central, with branches off to Birmingham New Street; Holyhead, Manchester Piccadilly, Liverpool Lime Street and Edinburgh Waverley. Traffic on this route consists of high speed passenger services and freight.
target: 大枢纽铁路于1837年开通，连接伯明翰市与利物浦和曼彻斯特铁路。如今，这条线路已成为繁忙的西海岸干线（WCML）的一部分，该干线从伦敦尤斯顿站延伸至格拉斯哥中央车站，并设有通往伯明翰新街站、霍利黑德站、曼彻斯特皮卡迪利站、利物浦莱姆街站和爱丁堡韦弗利站的支线。该线路的交通主要包括高速客运和货运。

source: The Grand Junction Railway, opened in 1837, connected the city of Birmingham to the Liverpool and Manchester railway. Today, this route is a part of the very busy WCML running from London Euston to Glasgow Central, with branches off to Birmingham New Street; Holyhead, Manchester Piccadilly, Liverpool Lime Street and Edinburgh Waverley. Traffic on this route consists of high speed passenger services and freight.
target: 大枢纽铁路于1837年开通，连接伯明翰市与利物浦和曼彻斯特铁路。如今，这条线路已成为繁忙的西海岸干线（WCML）的一部分，该干线从伦敦尤斯顿站延伸至格拉斯哥中央车站，并设有通往伯明翰新街站、霍利黑德站、曼彻斯特皮卡迪利站、利物浦莱姆街站和爱丁堡韦弗利站的支线。该线路的交通主要包括高速客运和货运。

source: The West Coast Mainline: Birmingham to Crewe route for Train Sim World recreates this busy mainline between Birmingham New Street in the south to Crewe in the north, winding its way through Wolverhampton and Stafford. The route features many places of interest including: Birmingham New Street, Soho Depot, Wolverhampton Steel Terminal, Oxley Depot and Crewe Basford Hall.

source: The original batch. Built between 2004 and 2005 by Siemens in Germany, the Class 350/1 units are unique in that they can run on 25kV AC overhead wires through their pantograph and on 750V DC third rail through their shoes. This is because the units were surplus from a Class 450 order. All Class 350 units have a maximum speed of 110mph (177 km/h).
target: 首批350/1型列车由德国西门子公司于2004年至2005年间制造，其独特之处在于，它既可以通过受电弓使用25千伏交流架空电线供电，也可以通过受电弓底座使用750伏直流第三轨供电。这是因为这些列车是450型列车订单的剩余部分。所有350型列车的最高时速均为110英里/小时（177公里/小时）。

source: You've just signed on at Crewe Carriage Sidings to undertake this morning's training exercise. Before you board your train, you need to make sure all the manual junctions are set. Follow the marker to the manual junction and make sure they're set correctly.
